# Development Workflow

## Setup
1. Install all dependencies: `npm run install:all`
2. Run both frontend and backend: `npm run dev:full`

## Key Scripts
- `npm run start:backend` - Start just the backend server
- `npm run start:frontend` - Start just the frontend dev server
- `npm run seed:all` - Seed the database with sample data
- `npm run db:reset` - Reset the database

## Database Operations
- [backend/src/seed](mdc:backend/src/seed) - Contains database seed scripts
- Database file: [backend/task.db](mdc:backend/task.db)

## API Testing
- Test API endpoints: [backend/test-api.js](mdc:backend/test-api.js)
